<h2>Vertical and horizontal navigation blocks</h2>

<p>
    The nav blocks can have a horizontal and vertical layout. Both of that types, can have
    a fancy stack of three color themes: <samp>.nav-bordered</samp>, <samp>.nav-light</samp>
    and, of course, <samp>.nav-dark</samp>. Notice, how stretchy looks those items of <samp>.nav-horizontal.stretch</samp>.
</p>

<div class="grid-12">
    <div class="span-8">
        <nav class="nav-horizontal nav-bordered" style="margin-bottom: 29px">
            <a href="#">Item 1</a>
